entries.title: Jury finds Musk, Tesla not liable in securities fraud trial following 'funding secured' tweets
entries.description: Tesla CEO Elon Musk was found not liable in a shareholder class-action suit stemming from 2018 tweets in which he said he was considering taking Tesla private.

entries.title: Jim Cramer says strong January jobs report shows the economy can handle more rate hikes
entries.description: Jim Cramer gave his thoughts on the January jobs report and what it reveals about the economy.
